01:06.233 --> 01:08.224
-Fuck you.
-That can be arranged.

01:08.402 --> 01:10.984
But I'm gonna kill you first.

01:30.132 --> 01:31.588
Old teacher's pet was scared.

01:31.758 --> 01:33.134
Yeah, he got you, dude.

01:33.302 --> 01:35.463
Yeah, I was scared.

01:36.013 --> 01:37.924
Vampires are scary.

01:38.098 --> 01:39.838
Oh, how's that lip?

01:40.767 --> 01:42.473
It's okay.

01:42.644 --> 01:44.020
How's your nose?

01:46.940 --> 01:53.106
-Vampires are not a joke.
-No sense of humor.

01:59.703 --> 02:03.537
There's a war going on.

02:04.875 --> 02:08.038
And you're either on the dark side...

02:08.211 --> 02:10.372
...or you're on the side of the light.

02:10.547 --> 02:13.380
And there ain't no in-between.

02:15.010 --> 02:16.295
I think you broke my nose.

03:57.320 --> 04:00.448
I'm so sorry, Vampire Bill.
I know how this must look.

04:00.615 --> 04:03.152
-Get out of my house.
-Bill, do not hurt him.

04:03.326 --> 04:05.817
I swear, I wouldn't have let it
go any further.

04:05.996 --> 04:07.327
I said, get out of my house.

04:07.497 --> 04:09.488
-lt's my house too.
-Jessica, upstairs.

04:09.666 --> 04:12.749
-Okay, let's all just try to calm down.
-That's a really good idea.

04:12.919 --> 04:15.581
Are you gonna leave
or am I gonna have to throw you out...

04:15.756 --> 04:17.587
...through a window that is closed?

04:17.758 --> 04:20.750
-Bill, that is just rude.
-Sookie, I've got this.

04:20.927 --> 04:23.669
I'm going. I'm going.

04:24.514 --> 04:28.098
-I wasn't gonna do nothing.
-lt's not her that I'm protecting, son.

04:44.659 --> 04:46.365
I don't believe him for a minute.

04:54.878 --> 04:59.542
We established there was to be
no hunting in this house.

04:59.716 --> 05:03.174
Look, I know you feel like shit
because you had to make me...

05:03.345 --> 05:04.881
...and you should feel like shit.

05:05.764 --> 05:09.552
But guess what? I'd never even kissed
a boy before that.

05:10.602 --> 05:14.060
Meeting Hoyt's the only good thing
that's happened to me...

05:14.231 --> 05:16.062
...since my whole new life started.

05:16.650 --> 05:19.938
No, I'm not ready
for anything to happen too fast.

05:20.111 --> 05:23.194
I'd have been happy just to go on
kissing him all night long.

05:24.533 --> 05:27.900
Now, is it my fault my fangs come out
when | get turned on?

05:43.051 --> 05:45.838
I think I'm gonna like her.

05:46.012 --> 05:50.346
Sookie, do not make the mistake
of thinking you two can be girlfriends.

05:50.517 --> 05:53.850
-She is--
-Yeah, I get it. She's a vampire.

05:54.020 --> 05:56.352
Believe me,
I learned my lesson about that.

05:56.523 --> 05:59.105
But, Bill, I think we should take her
with us to Dallas.

05:59.276 --> 06:03.110
I think it would be good for you
because I think, deep down...

06:03.280 --> 06:06.113
...you don't like vampires,
even though you are one.

06:06.283 --> 06:07.739
So?

06:07.909 --> 06:10.241
Well, hating yourself is a bad thing.

06:11.162 --> 06:14.074
I am a vampire.
I am supposed to be tormented.

06:14.249 --> 06:18.208
You're not just a vampire.
And Jessica doesn't have to be either.

06:18.378 --> 06:21.962
You can teach her how to walk that line
between vampire and human.

06:22.132 --> 06:23.963
Yes, because I have mastered that.

06:24.885 --> 06:27.547
Okay, so you can teach each other.

06:30.849 --> 06:33.340
It's so different for her.

06:40.108 --> 06:41.894
When I was made, one had no choice...

06:42.068 --> 06:46.186
...but to live completely outside
the human world...

06:46.489 --> 06:48.480
...as an outlaw...

06:48.992 --> 06:50.732
...a hunter.

06:52.037 --> 06:55.074
Humans were prey and nothing else.

06:58.126 --> 07:00.412
