for two travel coffins instead ofjust one.

07:12.599 --> 07:17.844
Isn't it exciting? Our first trip together.

07:18.688 --> 07:20.770
Oh, come on, Bill.

07:20.941 --> 07:23.227
l was almost killed last night.

07:23.401 --> 07:25.312
