07:38.792 --> 07:41.454
-So you do this a lot?
-Swim?

07:41.628 --> 07:44.620
Well, at night.

07:45.173 --> 07:47.084
Actually, I do.

07:48.301 --> 07:50.041
I love when it's dark.

07:50.220 --> 07:53.132
