09:17.265 --> 09:19.256
Cities bring out
the worst in people.

09:19.434 --> 09:21.425
They lose touch with nature.

09:21.603 --> 09:23.685
It's where they come from.

09:25.565 --> 09:27.806
People do that here too.

09:27.984 --> 09:29.815
Not in the same way.

09:34.699 --> 09:38.817
My fingertips are turning into raisins
and | feel like pancakes.

09:39.496 --> 09:42.704
There's a 24-hour truck stop
out on l-20 toward Arcadia...

09:42.874 --> 09:44.830
